highlights.text: “Baila de Gasolina” by Effe Serieus has been on Viral Songs Netherlands the longest, at 202 days straight.
Beste Zangers has the most spots on Viral Songs Netherlands. “Kan Je Me Zien” is the highest at #2.
“Unbind” by Eloi Youssef is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Netherlands at #1.
“Freeze” by Meadow and Junior Songfestival is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Netherlands, up 2 spots at #12.
